{
  "chapter": 126,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"生离死别\"，是全书最悲惨的高潮之一。苏樱与铁心兰在树下对话，铁心兰透露花无缺已自杀身亡——她求花无缺不要杀小鱼儿，花无缺答应后选择自尽。铁心兰也已服下剧毒，托付苏樱将她与花无缺合葬，并请苏樱照顾小鱼儿后安然死去。与此同时，小鱼儿与花无缺激战七百招后，怜星宫主试图揭露二人是孪生兄弟的秘密，却被邀月宫主以寒冰掌力制住。决斗中花无缺本想故意送死让小鱼儿获胜，但小鱼儿弄巧成拙反被打成重伤身亡。邀月宫主疯狂揭露真相——花无缺与小鱼儿是江枫的孪生子，她等了二十年就是为了看兄弟自相残杀。花无缺在悲痛中拔出魔剑\"碧血照丹心\"欲自尽，却被神秘人夺去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "你也在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "他……他已死了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "小鱼儿没有死，你哭什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "小鱼儿没有死？死的难道是花无缺？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "我不信，小鱼儿是绝不会杀花无缺的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "不是他杀死了花无缺，而是花无缺杀死了自己。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "他杀死了自己？为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "因为……因为我求他莫要杀小鱼儿，他答应了我，自己只有死……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "你明知花无缺只有一死，还要求他莫要杀死小鱼儿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "花无缺明知如此，还是答应了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "他本就是世上最伟大的人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "但你为了小鱼儿，而不惜要这最伟大的人死？想不到你对小鱼儿的情感竟如此深厚……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "但我真心爱着的并不是小鱼儿。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "不是小鱼儿，难道是花无缺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "不错，我……我爱的是他，全心全意地爱他，你永远不知道我现在爱他有多深，没有人知道我爱他有多深。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "但你却要他死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "不错，因为我已决心要陪着他一起死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "你这是为了什么呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "因为我爱上了花无缺，花无缺也爱上了我，我觉得我们都对不起小鱼儿，所以我们只有死……只有以死才能报答他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "我还是不懂，虽然我也是女人，却还是不懂你的心意，难怪男人都说女人的心比海底的针更难捉摸了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "你怎么样了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "现在他已死了，我也要死了，我们立刻就要相聚，世上所有丑恶残酷，痛苦的事，再也不能伤害到我们。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "胡说，你不会死的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "我已服下世上最毒的毒药，已是非死不可的了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_nv_shi",
      "speaker_name": "萧女史",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "可惜呀，可惜！这两个孩子都是百年难遇的武林奇才，无论谁死了都可惜得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_shi_ba",
      "speaker_name": "祢十八",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这就叫造化弄人……造化弄人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "住手，我有话说。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "怜星宫主",
      "text": "你有什么话说？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "大姐，二十年前的事，已过去很久了，江枫他们虽然对不住你，可是……可是他们如今连尸骨都已化为飞灰，大姐，你……何必再恨他们呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "怜星宫主",
      "text": "你难道想饶了他们？你难道想要在此时说出他们的秘密？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "我只是想……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "怜星宫主",
      "text": "从你七岁的时候，就喜欢跟我捣蛋，无论我喜欢什么，你都要和我争一争，无论我想做什么，你都要想法子破坏。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "你……你莫忘了，我毕竟是你的妹妹。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "你疯了，你想干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "怜星宫主",
      "text": "我并没有疯，只不过，我等了二十年才等到今天，我绝不会再让任何人来破坏它，你也不能……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你看，这一战已快结束了，江枫和月奴若知道他们的孪生子正在自相残杀，一定会后悔昔日为何要做出那种事的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_xing_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "怜星宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你们莫要再打了，听见了吗？因为你们本是亲生的兄弟。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "我……我们总算是姊妹，现在我想求你一件事，不知道你答不答应？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "无论你要我做什么，只管说吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "我死了之后，希望你能将我和花无缺埋葬到一起，也希望你告诉小鱼儿，我虽然不能嫁给他，但我始终是他的姐姐，他的朋友。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "我……我答应你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "我也希望你好好照顾小鱼儿，他虽然是匹野马，但有你在他身旁，他也许会变得好一些的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "他会么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "listener_name": "苏樱",
      "text": "嗯，因为我很了解他，我知道他真心喜欢的，只有你一个人，至于我……他从没有喜欢过我，只不过因为他很好强很好胜……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "listener_name": "铁心兰",
      "text": "我知道，我全知道，求你莫要再说，无论你要我做什么，我都答应你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "listener_name": "小鱼儿",
      "text": "你……你明明可以避开那一招的，你……你……你……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "listener_name": "燕南天",
      "text": "我本想用这一招故意诱他上当的，谁知……谁知他……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "这只因我……我太聪明了，反而弄巧成拙……弄巧成拙……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "listener_name": "燕南天",
      "text": "方才我拉开了无缺，其实却是救了你，只因世上谁都可以杀他，只有你是万万杀不得他的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "listener_name": "燕南天",
      "text": "你可知道他是谁么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "告诉你，他也是江枫的儿子，他本是小鱼儿的孪生兄弟。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "放屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "listener_name": "燕南天",
      "text": "我等了二十年，就是在等今天，等他们兄弟自相残杀而死，我等了二十年，直到今天才能将这秘密说出来，我实在高兴极了，痛快极了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "listener_name": "邀月宫主",
      "text": "无论你怎么说，我连一个字都不相信。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "listener_name": "燕南天",
      "text": "我知道你会相信的，一定会相信的，你仔细一想，就会发觉他们俩人有多么相似，你再看看他们的眼睛，他们的鼻子……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你可知道我为什么要逼他们俩人动手？你可知道我为什么一定要花无缺亲手杀死小鱼儿？……你们本来一定想不通这道理，是吗？现在你们虽已明白，却已太迟了，太迟了……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "listener_name": "花无缺",
      "text": "你自己杀死了你自己的兄弟，你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "listener_name": "花无缺",
      "text": "你莫忘了，你身上还有一柄'碧血照丹心'，你现在总该相信这是柄魔剑了吧。无论谁得到它，都只有死！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "listener_name": "花无缺",
      "text": "现在你的时候已到了，你还等什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "你是谁？为什么不让我死？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 126,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    }
